1
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:21,320
[A week ago]

2
00:00:21,320 --> 00:00:21,650
Go.

3
00:00:21,650 --> 00:00:22,160
[Nanping City Prison]

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:23,510
And don't come back.

5
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,880
This is some high-end stuff.

6
00:00:51,940 --> 00:00:52,690
See you.

7
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,470
It's been ten years.

8
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:55,680
You've got an heir now, kid.

9
00:02:11,950 --> 00:02:12,710
Hou Jun.

10
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,030
Mr. Ma.

11
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:20,490
Look at my memory.

12
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:22,400
I figured you'd be getting out these days.

13
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:24,430
I even wanted to pick you up.
But I got busy and forgot.

14
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:25,100
Alright, alright,

15
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:26,490
Long time no see.

16
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:29,290
Come on, come on. Let's talk in my office.

17
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:35,590
You look pretty good.

18
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:36,260
You look sharp.

19
00:02:36,260 --> 00:02:37,920
That's thanks to you, Mr. Ma.

20
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:39,590
Everything you told me to handle before,

21
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:40,720
I keep it all in mind.

22
00:02:44,829 --> 00:02:47,910
I heard Xia Xue is with you now.

23
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:49,020
Yes.

24
00:02:49,890 --> 00:02:51,150
I felt sorry for her.

25
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:53,230
And the kid needs to be cared for.

26
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,420
The child is being well looked after.

27
00:02:57,390 --> 00:02:58,120
That's good.

28
00:02:58,730 --> 00:03:00,270
If you have time someday,

29
00:03:00,750 --> 00:03:01,840
I can arrange it,

30
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,100
and you two can meet up.

31
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:07,080
As long as the kid's happy, that's enough.

32
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,110
I'll just

33
00:03:09,130 --> 00:03:11,010
take a look from afar.

34
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:18,640
Now that I'm out after serving
my sentence, I still have things to do.

35
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:20,070
Alright.

36
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:23,120
If you need anything,
just tell me anytime.

37
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:25,750
By the way,

38
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:30,070
this is all the cash I have today.

39
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,470
Take it.

40
00:03:31,470 --> 00:03:33,120
I am not here to ask you for money.

41
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,190
I know, I know.

42
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:34,960
No, no, no.

43
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,360
Take it. Please take it.

44
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,240
No, no, no.

45
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:39,840
Take it.

46
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,120
If you run into any trouble,

47
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:41,910
just tell me,

48
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:42,960
Mr. Ma.

49
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:25,980
[THE GUILTY]

50
00:05:26,220 --> 00:05:32,180
[Episode 12]

51
00:05:39,610 --> 00:05:44,480
[Grave of Beloved Son Li Jianjun]

52
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:02,930
Hello, have you seen Jianjun?

53
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:04,720
Hello, have you seen Li Jianjun?

54
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,920
Have you seen Li Jianjun—

55
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,160
Come on, let me do it.

56
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,330
Li Jianjun!

57
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,740
You've taken the ring.

58
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:24,940
We're family now.

59
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,920
Give me two jins.

60
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,430
Here you are, sir.

61
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:50,960
Don't buy it.
I told you I don't like kumquats.

62
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:52,680
You have to eat some.

63
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,040
How can you skip fruit?

64
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,780
He was my fiancé.

65
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:25,090
He also worked at the shipyard.

66
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:28,760
He used to love buying kumquats for me.

67
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,980
But I didn't like them.

68
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:34,290
I'd always secretly put them back.

69
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,330
I still don't like them now.

70
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:43,070
But every time I eat one, I think of him.

71
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:47,650
People forget easily.

72
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:51,870
If some things aren't
deliberately reminded,

73
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,840
they're easy to forget.

74
00:07:59,070 --> 00:07:59,830
Some things

75
00:08:01,110 --> 00:08:02,370
don't need reminders.

76
00:08:03,370 --> 00:08:05,700
You'll never forget them your whole life.

77
00:08:13,940 --> 00:08:14,730
Speak.

78
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:17,760
What do you want to talk to me about?

79
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,360
I always thought

80
00:08:23,530 --> 00:08:26,530
the shipyard explosion ten years ago
was an accident.

81
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,510
But now,

82
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:32,250
I think there may be
something else behind it.

83
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:35,830
If it's classified as a criminal case,

84
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:38,659
that means the real culprit

85
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:41,049
has been hidden for ten years.

86
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:45,840
What do you mean
by telling me all this?

87
00:08:47,230 --> 00:08:49,230
I want to cooperate with the police.

88
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,790
You don't have to be so surprised.

89
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:55,850
I've wanted to do this for a long time.

90
00:08:56,930 --> 00:08:58,530
How do you plan to cooperate?

91
00:08:59,230 --> 00:09:01,360
You stay in the open; I stay in the dark.

92
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,870
I can provide you

93
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,840
with some leads on the shipyard explosion.

94
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:11,920
After the truth about the explosion
comes out,

95
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:14,260
you'll learn another truth.

96
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,600
What truth?

97
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:20,500
About Ma Ke's death.

98
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:26,360
I knew what you said yesterday
wasn't the truth.

99
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,890
But you can't find evidence

100
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:30,440
to overturn my testimony, can you?

101
00:09:31,510 --> 00:09:33,390
Yes, that's right.

102
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:36,030
So I don't understand

103
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:39,520
why, after finally clearing your name,

104
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:42,200
you still want to wade into this mess.

105
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:49,680
Because in that cemetery,

106
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:52,460
someone I knew is also buried,

107
00:09:54,170 --> 00:09:55,830
and I need to give him justice.

108
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:02,600
That's the real reason you came to me,
isn't it?

109
00:10:05,150 --> 00:10:05,980
Speak.

110
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,340
What have you found so far?

111
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:13,080
I remembered something strange

112
00:10:15,060 --> 00:10:16,270
from ten years ago.

113
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,120
Whose car is that?

114
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,580
I've never seen it before.

115
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:27,560
You throwing shade at me?

116
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,790
Isn't your tricycle good enough?

117
00:10:31,820 --> 00:10:33,060
It's just a Santana.

118
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,740
When I become a lawyer someday,
I'll buy you one.

119
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:38,360
Alright, then I'll wait for your car.

120
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:39,670
Hurry up.

121
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:40,840
Xia Xue is waiting.

122
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,630
Later, I noticed

123
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,440
that after the shipyard explosion,

124
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,800
that car stayed inside the yard.

125
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:54,000
I thought it was suspicious,

126
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,080
so I checked the vehicle entry records.

127
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,570
I found that one week
before the explosion,

128
00:10:57,570 --> 00:10:58,480
a car

129
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,740
often entered the shipyard as a visitor.

130
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,550
I suspect the owner of that car

131
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:03,960
died in the explosion.

132
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,140
After that, I used every means

133
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:08,100
to investigate who the owner was.

134
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,340
His name was Li Hai.

135
00:11:10,730 --> 00:11:12,330
He was from Mingshan County.

136
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:17,030
[Victim No. 13]

137
00:11:22,690 --> 00:11:24,290
You've told me a lot today,

138
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:26,360
but I think it's all speculation.

139
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:30,810
All that still needs to be verified.

140
00:11:31,050 --> 00:11:31,930
Of course.

141
00:11:34,630 --> 00:11:35,960
After all, I'm not a cop.

142
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,880
How's the investigation going?

143
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:57,870
We found something.

144
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:59,030
The owner was named Li Hai.

145
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:00,360
He's been missing for many years.

146
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,960
His wife was named Li Fengxia

147
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,270
and was from Mingshan County.

148
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:05,550
She died accidentally in October 1999.

149
00:12:05,550 --> 00:12:06,950
Judging by the timeline,

150
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,670
Li Fengxia's time of death

151
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:10,910
was right after the shipyard explosion.

152
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:11,370
Wen,

153
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,360
could Li Fengxia have been silenced?

154
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,220
Anything else?

155
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:17,080
Did you find the address?

156
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,080
Yes.

157
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,340
I'll send it to you now.

158
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:22,120
Alright, got it.

159
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,440
I'll contact you if there's any update.

160
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,200
Okay, Wen.

161
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,660
You and Yunpeng stay safe.

162
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:29,640
Don't worry.

163
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,970
Wen, have something to eat.

164
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:45,830
I'll pass. You eat.

165
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:00,910
Go.

166
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,260
Go.

167
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,550
Bye-bye.

168
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,000
Ma Derong.

169
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,480
What on earth do you want?

170
00:13:58,180 --> 00:13:59,580
I miss my granddaughter.

171
00:14:00,070 --> 00:14:01,140
I want to see her.

172
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:03,270
Don't come here to see her again.

173
00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:04,390
Or I'll call the police.

174
00:14:04,390 --> 00:14:05,720
None of us will end well.

175
00:14:16,470 --> 00:14:17,590
Xia Xue,

176
00:14:19,340 --> 00:14:20,790
let me give you a warning.

177
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,480
Wen.

178
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:36,790
That's about it. Let's settle the bill.

179
00:14:36,790 --> 00:14:37,360
Okay.

180
00:14:51,100 --> 00:14:52,200
It's done? Let's go.

181
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:52,730
Let's go.

182
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:12,510
Wen.

183
00:15:12,910 --> 00:15:14,310
No need. You drink first.

184
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,780
The brakes failed.

185
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:38,100
The car was tampered with.

186
00:15:38,270 --> 00:15:39,720
Wu, hold on tight.

187
00:15:41,230 --> 00:15:42,080
Got it.

188
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:11,320
Wu, hold on tight!

189
00:16:18,890 --> 00:16:22,350
[Nanping Bo'ai International Hospital]

190
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,770
Someone's made a move against you.

191
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,500
You coming to see me

192
00:16:39,020 --> 00:16:40,560
means it wasn't you.

193
00:16:40,870 --> 00:16:41,600
Obviously,

194
00:16:41,940 --> 00:16:43,270
someone doesn't want you
to go to Mingshan County

195
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:44,470
to investigate Li Hai.

196
00:16:44,470 --> 00:16:47,000
That proves your current direction
is right.

197
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:49,560
And it also means

198
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:53,010
someone already knows
your line of investigation.

199
00:16:53,670 --> 00:16:55,120
Have you ever thought about

200
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:57,250
who leaked
your movements in advance?

201
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:07,640
He,

202
00:17:08,510 --> 00:17:09,380
do me a favor.

203
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:10,400
What is it?

204
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:13,160
Take a look at this person.
Do you recognize him?

205
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:14,180
Let me remind you,

206
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:17,380
Li Hai was arrested multiple times
for drug use.

207
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:17,940
Chang,

208
00:17:17,990 --> 00:17:19,050
help me find anyone

209
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:21,750
who had contact with drug kingpins
in Nanping ten years ago.

210
00:17:21,750 --> 00:17:22,339
Alright.

211
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:23,540
I'll ask around.

212
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:24,880
Do me a favor.

213
00:17:26,069 --> 00:17:26,920
Do me a favor.

214
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,480
Do you recognize this person?

215
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:29,920
No.

216
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:30,850
I don't know him.

217
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:31,980
You don't know him?

218
00:17:32,150 --> 00:17:34,270
You've seen so many people,
you must know him.

219
00:17:34,270 --> 00:17:35,720
Look carefully again.

220
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:38,720
Mr. Chang, I really haven't seen him.

221
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,050
I really don't know him.

222
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:42,960
Alright, sorry to bother you.

223
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:43,750
I'm leaving.

224
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:50,640
Mr. Chang.

225
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:52,030
Feng.

226
00:17:57,030 --> 00:17:58,160
Isn't this Li Hai?

227
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:02,740
Ten years ago, he used
to pick up from Qiu.

228
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:04,200
You sure?

229
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:06,000
After Qiu got locked up,

230
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,740
I never saw him again.

231
00:18:09,300 --> 00:18:09,720
[Harmony Brings Prosperity]

232
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:10,400
Mr. Chang.

233
00:18:15,030 --> 00:18:16,030
Call him Mr. Ming.

234
00:18:18,270 --> 00:18:18,960
Mr. Ming.

235
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,240
You know Li Hai?

236
00:18:23,750 --> 00:18:24,550
Yeah.

237
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:25,890
What do you need?

238
00:18:26,550 --> 00:18:27,350
Where is he?

239
00:18:28,030 --> 00:18:29,400
He's

240
00:18:31,310 --> 00:18:32,640
hard to find now.

241
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,770
What do you want to know?

242
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,690
Where did he go?

243
00:18:49,550 --> 00:18:50,960
I want to know too.

244
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:52,680
He still owes me money.

245
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:54,390
Besides his wife,

246
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:56,120
who else could contact him?

247
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:57,830
Actually,

248
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,590
there is one.

249
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:02,720
A woman.

250
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:03,920
Her name is...

251
00:19:04,130 --> 00:19:05,650
Chen Yan.

252
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,640
Li Hai's wife

253
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:09,010
couldn't have kids.

254
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:11,460
Later, he got together with Chen Yan.

255
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:13,680
She got pregnant with his child.

256
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:15,710
Come on, son. Time to eat.

257
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:20,390
After he found out,

258
00:19:20,410 --> 00:19:22,510
he wanted to divorce his wife
and be with Chen Yan.

259
00:19:22,510 --> 00:19:23,920
But unexpectedly,

260
00:19:24,310 --> 00:19:25,830
the child was born

261
00:19:27,790 --> 00:19:29,000
with mental issues.

262
00:19:40,250 --> 00:19:41,780
Later I heard

263
00:19:42,030 --> 00:19:44,000
Li Hai went missing years ago,

264
00:19:44,090 --> 00:19:45,640
and his wife also died.

265
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:48,930
And Chen Yan was left
to raise the child alone.

266
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:52,720
Her place

267
00:19:53,020 --> 00:19:55,650
is near the embankment in Beishan Village.

268
00:20:20,290 --> 00:20:21,350
Have another bite.

269
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:23,640
Who is it?

270
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:41,250
Who are you looking for?

271
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:44,970
Is this Chen Yan's home?

272
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:46,530
Chen Yan is my wife.

273
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:47,480
Who are you?

274
00:20:50,290 --> 00:20:51,820
I want to ask her something.

275
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,540
She's not here.

276
00:20:55,430 --> 00:20:57,430
Just a few questions and I'll leave.

277
00:20:58,510 --> 00:20:59,590
Wait a moment.

278
00:21:00,900 --> 00:21:03,580
Zhuang, go inside first
and wait for me, okay?

279
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:07,200
After I finish talking with the guest,
I'll play with you.

280
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:10,860
Come in.

281
00:21:11,830 --> 00:21:12,380
Okay.

282
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:45,920
Run!

283
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:20,420
Do you know

284
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:23,160
why those two people wanted to kill you?

285
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:26,810
They rushed in and attacked
without saying a word.

286
00:22:31,830 --> 00:22:33,550
They came because of Li Hai.

287
00:22:38,080 --> 00:22:40,800
How much do you know about him?

288
00:22:47,190 --> 00:22:48,040
Get lost!

289
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:52,030
Eating my food, drinking my stuff,

290
00:22:52,030 --> 00:22:54,160
just thinking about it makes me angry!

291
00:22:56,980 --> 00:22:59,040
Stop crying! What are you crying for?

292
00:22:59,830 --> 00:23:00,790
I don't know.

293
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:04,350
All these years, you never looked for him?

294
00:23:04,630 --> 00:23:05,830
How was I supposed to?

295
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:07,150
Call the police?

296
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:08,960
I wasn't his family.

297
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:10,760
What would I even say to the police?

298
00:23:10,760 --> 00:23:12,690
Even if I did, what good would it do?

299
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:14,000
If his wife hadn't looked for him,

300
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,660
maybe she wouldn't have died.

301
00:23:17,220 --> 00:23:19,020
Do you know how his wife died?

302
00:23:19,790 --> 00:23:21,320
That, I don't know, either.

303
00:23:25,790 --> 00:23:27,120
Before he disappeared,

304
00:23:27,690 --> 00:23:29,180
did he contact anyone

305
00:23:30,070 --> 00:23:31,030
or meet anyone?

306
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:33,990
We were close,

307
00:23:35,750 --> 00:23:38,010
but he rarely talked about his business.

308
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:44,790
But the last time,
before he went to Nanping,

309
00:23:44,790 --> 00:23:46,310
he got drunk and bragged

310
00:23:47,070 --> 00:23:50,640
about knowing some guy named Mr. Yi

311
00:23:51,450 --> 00:23:53,310
who could help him strike it rich.

312
00:23:54,420 --> 00:23:55,620
What's his full name?

313
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:03,720
Ming, so you finally
remembered to call me?

314
00:24:03,870 --> 00:24:05,870
Uncle San, let me ask you something.

315
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:06,760
What is it?

316
00:24:07,130 --> 00:24:10,000
Have you ever heard
of a "Mr. Yi" in Nanping

317
00:24:10,030 --> 00:24:10,680
about ten years back?

318
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:12,140
I don't know his real name.

319
00:24:12,460 --> 00:24:13,860
I think there was a guy like that.

320
00:24:13,860 --> 00:24:15,030
Then please help me check.

321
00:24:15,030 --> 00:24:15,960
It's urgent.

322
00:24:15,960 --> 00:24:17,570
Alright, I'll look into it.

323
00:24:37,350 --> 00:24:38,550
Xia Xue,

324
00:24:39,530 --> 00:24:41,270
let me give you a warning.

325
00:24:42,770 --> 00:24:45,450
When I went inside back then,
I kept thinking

326
00:24:46,940 --> 00:24:49,820
who wanted to set me up like that.

327
00:24:51,530 --> 00:24:52,850
When I got out,

328
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:54,800
I finally figured it out.

329
00:24:54,850 --> 00:24:55,720
Besides you,

330
00:24:56,900 --> 00:24:58,760
there was someone else behind it.

331
00:24:59,320 --> 00:25:00,780
What are you trying to say?

332
00:25:06,190 --> 00:25:07,360
After I went inside,

333
00:25:07,380 --> 00:25:09,290
who benefited the most?

334
00:25:29,340 --> 00:25:31,050
Let me give you another clue.

335
00:25:31,720 --> 00:25:33,120
There's a man named Xu Yi.

336
00:25:33,600 --> 00:25:34,930
He was Li Hai's handler.

337
00:25:35,870 --> 00:25:39,130
Ten years ago in Nanping,
on the surface, he did smuggling,

338
00:25:39,350 --> 00:25:42,430
but in reality he dealt in gambling,
prostitution, and drugs.

339
00:25:42,430 --> 00:25:43,660
He's the kind of man

340
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:46,040
who would do anything for money.

341
00:25:48,370 --> 00:25:49,640
That's all I know.

342
00:25:51,260 --> 00:25:53,520
Because three years ago, he went inside.

343
00:25:57,350 --> 00:25:58,160
Hello, Wu.

344
00:25:58,600 --> 00:26:00,700
Check on an inmate named Xu Yi for me.

345
00:26:01,270 --> 00:26:03,130
He went to prison three years ago.

346
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:14,110
Ms. Wen.

347
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:15,880
Everything ready?

348
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:16,790
Yes.

349
00:26:16,810 --> 00:26:18,060
Are you alright?

350
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:19,840
Just some minor scrapes.

351
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:20,490
Let's go.

352
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:25,450
Captain Qin.

353
00:26:35,120 --> 00:26:35,920
Hey, man.

354
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:38,030
I've said everything I needed to say.

355
00:26:38,030 --> 00:26:39,260
I've been sentenced, too.

356
00:26:39,260 --> 00:26:40,220
What do you mean?

357
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:42,050
Nothing.

358
00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:44,540
We're just here today

359
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:46,530
to ask about something.

360
00:26:47,270 --> 00:26:48,160
About what?

361
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:52,720
Li Hai.

362
00:26:55,030 --> 00:26:55,960
I don't know him.

363
00:26:56,800 --> 00:26:58,000
Don't rush to answer.

364
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,400
Take your time and think.

365
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:01,070
I don't know him.
How am I supposed

366
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:03,070
to remember someone I've never met?

367
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:05,750
Xu Yi, let me tell you.

368
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:09,200
Before we came to interrogate you today,

369
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:12,070
we were already prepared.

370
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:14,270
Wait, Officer,

371
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:16,310
please don't scare me like that.

372
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,920
I'm not scaring you.

373
00:27:18,510 --> 00:27:20,240
Let me tell you something else.

374
00:27:20,350 --> 00:27:21,720
Before I came today,

375
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:23,830
I already let this information out.

376
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:26,030
No matter who you're covering for,

377
00:27:26,030 --> 00:27:27,790
or what you're trying to hide,

378
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:30,490
I think that person already knows.

379
00:27:33,750 --> 00:27:35,450
If that's the case,

380
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:38,160
then I'm even less likely to say anything.

381
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:40,420
Whether you talk or not isn't important.

382
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:43,400
What matters is that we came to see you.

383
00:27:44,180 --> 00:27:45,960
To that person,

384
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:48,020
we've already traced the case to you.

385
00:27:48,310 --> 00:27:49,830
It doesn't matter to us.

386
00:27:49,850 --> 00:27:51,810
This case will
be cracked sooner or later.

387
00:27:51,810 --> 00:27:55,140
But do you really think what comes after
will be easy for you?

388
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:03,200
If you trust us police,

389
00:28:04,510 --> 00:28:06,400
I can guarantee you this:

390
00:28:07,270 --> 00:28:09,200
I can apply for protection for you,

391
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:12,480
even a prison transfer.

392
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:14,280
So if you still don't talk today,

393
00:28:14,510 --> 00:28:17,240
the next people who come
to see you might not be us.

394
00:28:26,310 --> 00:28:28,240
You can't remember him at all, huh?

395
00:28:29,790 --> 00:28:31,140
That's fine. Let's go.

396
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,240
Wait, wait.

397
00:28:37,880 --> 00:28:39,440
Li Hai was working for me.

398
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:41,720
What kind of work?

399
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:44,000
As long as he got paid,

400
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:45,070
he'd do anything.

401
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:46,520
He used drugs.

402
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:50,170
And he had a mentally challenged son.

403
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:52,400
I gave him all the dirty work.

404
00:28:55,270 --> 00:28:57,160
Did you order him to carry out

405
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:59,760
the Nanping Shipyard explosion
ten years ago?

406
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:06,510
Lin Hua,

407
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:08,440
you have to keep the ring thing
confidential for me.

408
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:09,710
Don't worry.

409
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:12,020
When are you planning to propose?

410
00:29:12,770 --> 00:29:13,740
Soon.

411
00:29:22,070 --> 00:29:23,440
Why aren't you wearing a helmet?

412
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:25,040
Which workshop are you from?

413
00:29:26,510 --> 00:29:27,200
Stop!

414
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:28,550
Stop!

415
00:29:30,350 --> 00:29:31,590
It's going to explode!

416
00:29:31,590 --> 00:29:33,720
It's going to explode! Run!

417
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:35,070
It's going to explode!

418
00:29:35,070 --> 00:29:35,920
What explosion?

419
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:37,180
It's going to explode!

420
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:46,800
Why blow up the shipyard?

421
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:48,400
It wasn't my idea.

422
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:50,460
Someone came to me and told me to do it.

423
00:29:52,240 --> 00:29:53,110
Who?

424
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,920
I really don't know who he was.

425
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:01,000
But

426
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:05,030
he worked for the government,
just like you.

427
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:07,480
Xu Yi.

428
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:08,980
Do you know what crime it is

429
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:11,120
to frame a state official
and give false testimony?

430
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:13,030
If I don't talk, you force me to.

431
00:30:13,070 --> 00:30:14,800
If I talk, you don't believe me.

432
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:16,480
Either way, I'm dead.

433
00:30:17,310 --> 00:30:19,110
What's the point of lying to you?

434
00:30:27,050 --> 00:30:28,440
Notify the forensic department

435
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,040
to perform a DNA comparison

436
00:30:29,040 --> 00:30:30,310
[Nanping City Prison]

437
00:30:30,310 --> 00:30:31,240
on Body No. 13

438
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:32,170
and Li Hai's son.

439
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:39,440
Wu.

440
00:30:43,030 --> 00:30:44,760
Don't tell anyone about today.

441
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:51,310
Wen, can we trust what Xu Yi said?

442
00:30:58,100 --> 00:30:59,830
Then how do we investigate now?

443
00:31:08,490 --> 00:31:09,670
You're up so early?

444
00:31:10,550 --> 00:31:12,610
I haven't been sleeping well lately.

445
00:31:12,780 --> 00:31:14,270
You just think too much.

446
00:31:14,510 --> 00:31:16,110
Tonight I'll drink with you.

447
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:19,540
Where's Shanshan? Still asleep?

448
00:31:20,350 --> 00:31:21,280
She's sleeping.

449
00:31:23,720 --> 00:31:24,880
Being kids is great.

450
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:27,750
No matter how big the mess is,

451
00:31:27,770 --> 00:31:29,300
they forget it in a few days.

452
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:40,410
Drink your milk.

453
00:31:40,420 --> 00:31:40,880
Okay.

454
00:31:49,720 --> 00:31:50,980
Why aren't you eating?

455
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:53,580
I'll eat later.

456
00:32:00,910 --> 00:32:02,350
With so much that has happened recently

457
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:04,010
why don't you ask me anything?

458
00:32:05,350 --> 00:32:06,550
I have nothing to ask.

459
00:32:10,790 --> 00:32:13,190
You don't even ask
about me meeting Lu Ming?

460
00:32:14,830 --> 00:32:16,830
How many years have we been married?

461
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,160
Eight.

462
00:32:19,480 --> 00:32:20,070
Right.

463
00:32:21,210 --> 00:32:22,470
It's been eight years.

464
00:32:23,310 --> 00:32:25,370
We've been through so much together.

465
00:32:26,830 --> 00:32:28,890
Even though there was no major drama,

466
00:32:30,510 --> 00:32:32,400
we've lived in peace,

467
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:34,400
and the child is growing up healthy.

468
00:32:34,420 --> 00:32:35,550
That's good enough.

469
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:46,400
I met Ma Derong.

470
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:50,000
Ma Derong? What did he want with you?

471
00:32:52,550 --> 00:32:53,920
He said

472
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:58,930
the shipyard explosion
had something to do with you.

473
00:33:06,410 --> 00:33:08,300
I could've guessed he'd say that.

474
00:33:10,130 --> 00:33:11,460
Given his current situation,

475
00:33:11,460 --> 00:33:13,520
he wishes I'd drop dead immediately.

476
00:33:22,570 --> 00:33:23,330
Xia Xue.

477
00:33:26,500 --> 00:33:28,410
How did Ma Ke treat you back then?

478
00:33:32,750 --> 00:33:35,290
How did Ma Derong abuse you both?

479
00:33:37,780 --> 00:33:40,110
You haven't forgotten all that, have you?

480
00:33:48,720 --> 00:33:50,320
I don't need you to remind me.

481
00:33:50,860 --> 00:33:54,290
Right now, I just want to know
who killed my father.

482
00:33:55,850 --> 00:33:58,250
That case was already concluded back then.

483
00:33:59,110 --> 00:34:02,070
The shipyard explosion
was ruled an accident.

484
00:34:03,750 --> 00:34:06,790
It's all in the past, isn't it?

485
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:18,000
You eat, too.

486
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:18,960
It'll get cold.

487
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:22,699
I'll eat later.

488
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:30,440
[Police]

489
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,630
Is the meeting content ready?

490
00:34:31,630 --> 00:34:32,510
Yes.

491
00:34:33,150 --> 00:34:33,820
Chief Liu.

492
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:34,480
Mom Liu.

493
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:38,420
Didn't I approve your leave?

494
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:40,080
Why are you back at work again?

495
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:41,670
I have some leads

496
00:34:41,670 --> 00:34:43,330
on the shipyard explosion,

497
00:34:43,550 --> 00:34:45,480
so I'm here to hold a meeting today.

498
00:34:45,590 --> 00:34:46,469
I know.

499
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:49,400
I also know you've been in contact
with Lu Ming.

500
00:34:50,710 --> 00:34:51,760
How did you know that?

501
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,290
Everyone in the unit knows.

502
00:34:58,150 --> 00:34:59,150
Don't look at him.

503
00:34:59,650 --> 00:35:01,260
I'll be blunt.

504
00:35:01,880 --> 00:35:03,510
Don't make the whole unit think

505
00:35:03,510 --> 00:35:06,440
you're abusing your position
for personal reasons.

506
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:08,070
Captain Qin.

507
00:35:09,630 --> 00:35:11,130
We received a tip that Ma Derong

508
00:35:11,130 --> 00:35:12,790
is at a hotel on Dongfeng Road.

509
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:14,160
Alright, I know.

510
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:15,690
I'll go make the arrest.

511
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:25,060
Hello, Criminal Investigation Unit.

512
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:25,620
Lu Ming?

513
00:35:25,620 --> 00:35:26,370
[Nanping Police Bureau]

514
00:35:26,370 --> 00:35:28,070
Captain Qin's off on a mission.

515
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:28,880
What's up?

516
00:35:29,340 --> 00:35:33,570
[Police]

517
00:35:38,430 --> 00:35:41,150
Captain Qin, are you still

518
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:42,440
not fully recovered?

519
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:51,110
Wen.

520
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:53,710
I told you to rest at home
for a couple more days.

521
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:54,760
You just wouldn't listen.

522
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:56,880
You don't trust us to handle things?

523
00:36:28,510 --> 00:36:29,570
Chief Liu,

524
00:36:29,710 --> 00:36:30,440
why is it you?

525
00:36:30,550 --> 00:36:31,910
Captain Qin's off on a mission.

526
00:36:31,910 --> 00:36:34,640
Go on. What clues do you
have about the explosion?

527
00:36:38,110 --> 00:36:39,360
Do you know Xu Yi?

528
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:44,920
Back then, it was Xu Yi who told Li Hai

529
00:36:45,340 --> 00:36:47,400
to carry out the shipyard explosion.

530
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:49,610
And the man who pulled Xu Yi's strings

531
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:51,950
was the former Security Department Chief.

532
00:36:51,950 --> 00:36:53,680
That is, the current Chief Liu—

533
00:36:53,950 --> 00:36:54,510
You.

534
00:36:55,770 --> 00:36:57,840
Back then, you were responsible
for shipyard security.

535
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,010
You knew better

536
00:36:59,700 --> 00:37:01,380
than anyone where the safety risks were.

537
00:37:01,380 --> 00:37:02,810
The one who knew best wasn't me.

538
00:37:02,810 --> 00:37:04,140
It was Xia Xue's father.

539
00:37:04,290 --> 00:37:05,770
So you planned it long ago,

540
00:37:06,510 --> 00:37:07,710
to make Xia Xue's father take the blame,

541
00:37:07,710 --> 00:37:08,480
didn't you?

542
00:37:10,500 --> 00:37:13,070
Lu Ming, you'd better think carefully.

543
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:15,590
What you're saying now

544
00:37:15,590 --> 00:37:17,720
are baseless accusations against me.

545
00:37:19,690 --> 00:37:20,620
I have evidence.

546
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:22,360
Chief Liu.

547
00:37:26,090 --> 00:37:28,220
Captain Qin's suspicions were right.

548
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:29,910
There was never any tip about Ma Derong.

549
00:37:29,910 --> 00:37:31,000
She led the team out

550
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:32,360
just to see if you'd lose your nerve.

551
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:32,930
Lu Ming?

552
00:37:34,650 --> 00:37:36,280
Captain Qin's off on a mission.

553
00:37:36,280 --> 00:37:36,880
What's up?

554
00:37:37,670 --> 00:37:38,760
Alright, got it.

555
00:37:40,070 --> 00:37:41,000
What's going on?

556
00:37:41,030 --> 00:37:42,000
Lu Ming called.

557
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:44,000
He said he has clues about the explosion

558
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:46,600
and wants to hand them
to Captain Qin in person.

559
00:37:47,250 --> 00:37:49,800
Someone doesn't want us
to go to Mingshan County

560
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,730
to investigate the missing Li Hai.

561
00:37:52,110 --> 00:37:53,370
Have you thought about

562
00:37:53,630 --> 00:37:55,760
who leaked your movements in advance?

563
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:58,430
So you also think
there's a mole within the police.

564
00:37:58,430 --> 00:37:58,980
Who is it?

565
00:37:59,510 --> 00:38:01,960
He works for the government,
just like you.

566
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:04,000
The shipyard explosion

567
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:05,590
was years ago.

568
00:38:05,590 --> 00:38:07,000
It's ancient history now.

569
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:08,930
Why are you still obsessed with it?

570
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:11,070
Leak the news of my meeting

571
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,590
with Lu Ming to Liu Zhijun.

572
00:38:18,270 --> 00:38:20,140
If it really is a cop,

573
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:21,660
then not only I,

574
00:38:22,070 --> 00:38:23,530
but you would be in danger.

575
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:25,000
Don't rush. I have a plan.

576
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:30,730
We already investigated Xu Yi.

577
00:38:31,330 --> 00:38:32,940
At first, we only suspected you.

578
00:38:32,940 --> 00:38:34,400
We called you to the office

579
00:38:34,590 --> 00:38:36,590
just to let you know Lu Ming was here.

580
00:38:36,930 --> 00:38:37,880
If you didn't come,

581
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:39,880
our suspicion would've been wrong.

582
00:38:40,110 --> 00:38:42,240
We didn't expect you to actually come.

583
00:38:45,560 --> 00:38:48,220
So you and Captain Qin teamed up
to trick me, huh?

584
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:55,760
Fine.

585
00:38:58,790 --> 00:39:00,190
Isn't everyone here now?

586
00:39:34,550 --> 00:39:35,360
Hello.

587
00:39:35,630 --> 00:39:36,740
I'm at Hekou Pier.

588
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:39,150
Someone's been shot. Come quickly!

589
00:39:41,670 --> 00:39:43,040
Turn around, Ren Yi.

590
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:48,910
Officer Wu! Officer Wu.

591
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:49,880
Officer Wu.

592
00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:52,590
Officer Wu, the ambulance is on the way.

593
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:53,440
Officer Wu!

594
00:39:54,880 --> 00:39:56,010
Officer Wu, wake up!

595
00:39:56,770 --> 00:39:57,720
Officer Wu!

596
00:40:01,200 --> 00:40:04,710
[Police]

597
00:40:04,770 --> 00:40:09,040
[Restricted Dock Area: No Smoking
Or Open Flames]

598
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:35,420
[Police]
